
This code is designed to do a naive bayes classification using Binary abd tern frequecy methods of prior probability calculation.

Prerequisites:

In order to run the code put the code as well the train and test data in a single directory.

Test File Name should be: test
Training File Name Should be : train

Python Interpreter: This code was developed for Python 2.7. Using Python 3.4 may break the code.

Command Execution:

>python BayesClassifier.py



